Class ChooseDependableStructureElementPropertyDescriptor

java.lang.Object

          de.hu.gralog.beans.propertydescriptor.ChooseDependableStructureElementPropertyDescriptor
All Implemented Interfaces:
DependsOnPropertyPropertyDescriptor
public class ChooseDependableStructureElementPropertyDescriptor
extends PropertyDescriptor
implements DependsOnPropertyPropertyDescriptor

This class is a special PropertyDescriptor to define properties of algorithms, structures, vertices and edges in GrALoG. This descriptor allows the user to choose an element ( elements are either vertices or edges ) of a structure, which is specified as another property of the same Bean, i.e. the bean for the structure, algorithm, vertex or edge. Always make sure that the property this descriptor depends on is of type Structure and that the property defined by this descriptor has the right type according to whether it is a vertex or an edge.

Author:
ordyniak
